  E'# Ã‡oxhÉ™dlilÉ™r vÉ™ Vuruqlara AyÄ±rma\n\n## Kurikulum Konteksti\n11-ci sinif, I BÃ¶lmÉ™ - Ã‡oxhÉ™dlilÉ™r\n\n## Ã‡oxhÉ™dli NÉ™dir?\n\nBir  neÃ§É™ hÉ™ddin toplandÄ±ÄŸÄ± cÉ™bri ifadÉ™dir.\n\n**MÉ™sÉ™lÉ™n:** P(x) = 3xÂ³ - 5xÂ² + 2x - 7\n\n**DÉ™rÉ™cÉ™:** Æn bÃ¶yÃ¼k dÉ™rÉ™cÉ™li hÉ™ddin dÉ™rÉ™cÉ™si (yuxarÄ±dakÄ± nÃ¼munÉ™dÉ™ 3)\n\n## Vuruqlara AyÄ±rma\n\nÃ‡oxhÉ™dlini vuruqlarÄ±n hasili ÅŸÉ™klindÉ™ yazmaq.\n\n**NÃ¼munÉ™:** xÂ² - 5x + 6 = (x - 2)(x - 3)\n\n## Vuruqlara AyÄ±rma ÃœsullarÄ±\n\n### 1. Ãœmumi Vuruq\n6xÂ³ - 9xÂ² = 3xÂ²(2x - 3)\n\n### 2. QÄ±sa Vurma DÃ¼sturlarÄ±\n\n- (a + b)Â² = aÂ² + 2ab + bÂ²\n- (a - b)Â² = aÂ² - 2ab + bÂ²\n- aÂ² - bÂ² = (a - b)(a + b)\n- aÂ³ + bÂ³ = (a + b)(aÂ² - ab + bÂ²)\n- aÂ³ - bÂ³ = (a - b)(aÂ² + ab + bÂ²)\n\n### 3. QruplaÅŸdÄ±rma\nxÂ³ + xÂ² + x + 1 = xÂ²(x + 1) + 1(x + 1) = (x + 1)(xÂ² + 1)\n\n### 4. KÃ¶k Tapma\n\nÆgÉ™r P(a) = 0 olarsa, (x - a) vuruqdur.\n\n## Bezout Teoremi\n\nP(x) Ã§oxhÉ™dlisini (x - a)-ya bÃ¶lmÉ™yÉ™dÉ™n qalÄ±q P(a)-ya bÉ™rabÉ™rdir.\n\n## Rasional KÃ¶klÉ™rin TapÄ±lmasÄ±\n\nÆgÉ™r p/q rasional kÃ¶kdirsÉ™:\n- p - sÉ™rbÉ™st hÉ™ddin bÃ¶lÉ™nlÉ™rindÉ™ndir\n- q - aparÄ±cÄ± É™msalÄ±n bÃ¶lÉ™nlÉ™rindÉ™ndir\n\n## NÃ¼munÉ™ MÉ™sÉ™lÉ™\n\n**MÉ™sÉ™lÉ™:** xÂ³ + 2xÂ² - 5x - 6 Ã§oxhÉ™dlisini vuruqlara ayÄ±rÄ±n.\n\n### HÉ™ll:\n\n1. MÃ¼mkÃ¼n kÃ¶klÉ™ri: Â±1, Â±2, Â±3, Â±6\n2. P(-1) = -1 + 2 + 5 - 6 = 0 âœ“ KÃ¶k!\n3. Horner sxemi ilÉ™ (x + 1)-É™ bÃ¶ldÃ¼k\n4. P(x) = (x + 1)(xÂ² + x - 6)\n5. xÂ² + x - 6 = (x - 2)(x + 3)\n6. **Cavab:** (x + 1)(x - 2)(x + 3)\n\n**KÃ¶klÉ™ri:** xâ‚ = -1, xâ‚‚ = 2, xâ‚ƒ = -3\n\n## Ev TapÅŸÄ±rÄ±qlarÄ±\n\n1. Vuruqlara ayÄ±rÄ±n:\n   - a) xÂ³ - 7x + 6\n   - b) xâ´ - 1\n   - c) xÂ³ + 3xÂ² - 4\n\n2. DÃ¼zbucaqlÄ±nÄ±n uzunluÄŸu enindÉ™n 3 sm Ã§ox, sahÉ™si 180 smÂ². Ã–lÃ§Ã¼lÉ™rini tapÄ±n.',
  'polynomial-factorizer',
